{"tid":346953,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求助]屋企有個爛賭撚可以點做?","createTime":"2017-08-04T11:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T12:03:22.000Z","uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aedccf481f72928073d0be007b75fd903705cf48","tid":346953,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:36:17.000Z","msg":"我阿爸係個死賭撚黎<br />\n<br />\n細細個開始就賭 賭輸唒自己D錢就拎阿媽既錢去賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母之後衰運毒要坐監, 坐完出黎同以前一撚樣<br />\n剩係識賭 我阿媽又蠢,成日信佢會改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日佢又拎唒老母D錢去澳門賭 又賭撚輸唒<br />\n屌真係好撚無助<br />\n有D咩方法先可以解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30e19bef3028d4857bdd4ab8bee7a814d5aea56","tid":346953,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:47:40.000Z","msg":"唔比家用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0498dd752028b92a450a676cb41415bd73d2d588","tid":346953,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"帶埋你阿媽走啦"},{"pid":"1679bcf91faf756433481caba14954842e117c4c","tid":346953,"uid":115060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:56:54.000Z","msg":"切左佢"},{"pid":"2d39ca9afad737e1f697ba724ed438a1826e2f65","tid":346953,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:57:56.000Z","msg":"你試下賭得勁過佢"},{"pid":"ef4eb11a64f0508807ae1c417732ff3019f29066","tid":346953,"uid":46061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:59:17.000Z","msg":"通常爛賭二都係輸<br />\n所以你見佢買咩就買對家<br />\n應該會贏到仆街"},{"pid":"2514c53981212898a9d271f998ed567aa5340800","tid":346953,"uid":9017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockqu